Use prepare_data.py to split existing data into train.jsonl and val.jsonl files
Export your openai api key
Upload these files to openai finetune job using this following commands:

openai api files.create --purpose fine-tune --file train.jsonl 
openai api files.create --purpose fine-tune --file val.jsonl 
Make note of the respective ids
After files are created, run the finetune job using this command: update the id;s of respective training file & val file

  openai api fine_tuning.jobs.create \
  -m gpt-4.1-mini-2025-04-14 \
  -F "file-EUUdhwntAqwhYuJxyXG8fx" \
  -V "file-18NafyV2CAWS4bfhhaJ8at"

Check status using the following command
openai api fine_tuning.jobs.retrieve -i ftjob-1DQFOfdkcRcOhvnf9Kg6xUT1

Get the data:
openai api fine_tuning.jobs.get -i ftjob-1DQFOfdkcRcOhvnf9Kg6xUT1

